values:
HELOOO i need warmer clothes. I'm trying to write a paper... FUCK THAT. Its Tuesday and we have a whole lotta school left, blows. Today was alright though, Hmmm i took a 2 hour nap at the nurses pad, then Gavin put a staple in my forearm, i didnt think he was serious, but he fucking lodged a staple in my skin. i pulled it out in 11th period and i kinda got blood everywhere, but i told my teacher i got stung by a bee. Went to Dons right after school, jamed, didnt do much, brendans new bass is the sickest thing though, way to go brendan, nerd. got home, took a nap, smacked a bitch, layed an egg, jumped on top of my refrigerator, my hands grew 20 times in diameter, pressed my clothing, drank, played some PIKIMIN. Jake is gay...oh yeah football friday. because its gonna be wet and awkward tommorow, CHEESE KIDS!! gerd.
oh yeah, how do i put pictures in this motha?

WHOOT. Christmas was alright, i had a better time with the people i was with then what i actually got, sounds dumb, but i didnt even get that much, besides Napoleon Dynomite & Pikmin 2. Yeah.. so its pretty much a fact that i havent been in a sobor state of mind for about 4 weeks, and going strong. Im looking foward for New Years, not sure whats gonna happen, but i know ill be having fun with some cool cats, and ill be ridiculisly fucked up. I really hope that i stop eating soon, i think im perminitly full, and sick. Oh yeah, Ryan Simmons' house was the best part of this break so far. good kids, good dutchies, good god.

SAY YOUR GOODBYES. nick is leaving thursday morning and he's going to florida, its sad, sooooo many good times with that kid, we were co-owners of matt fousadiouroris soul. WEll i just got back from Youth Group. IT WAS A FEAST. i hung out with zack's mom and don before we went, it was good. Played brendan in a little table tennis, brendan has bad knees, please dont worry. i have to build a bridge tonight but i dont wanna.. if only brendan were here. that worm. im out. WHAT UP.

Sup fools, soo Christmas is comming up and its all about giving, giving broken skulls and bloody eyes. I didnt do much today, took alittle nap, woke up glued some stuff, then i went to best buy.... yup. High School High, Em-Ef'n 5 dollars, you know it. Sooo yeah.. ive decided to go on strike, until someone gives me a hundred dollars, no fishing, no yelling (some yelling), no smelling, no running, no schoolwork, no respect. Someone is bound to be like "Holy Shit!! someone get this kid a hundred dollars!! He needs his Mushroom Fix." ..yeah anytime now. I found my digital camera, im gonna start taking pictures, i'll start off with cats, then ill work my way up to supreme court justices. fucking justice.

Well, its a Sunday night, and ive decided to create a Live Journal, just shows you how board i was today. I woke up around 11, went downstairs listened to Mr.Bungle and The Blood Brothers for quite some time. Then I started to paint moldings... today really sucked. Fuck. Tomorrow is Monday, and the same shit is going to happen..
